---
import DownloadButton from './DownloadButton.tsx';
---

<section id="about" class="py-16 px-6 border-t border-border">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="mb-6 text-text-muted">
      <span class="text-accent">$</span> ls about/
    </div>
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-8">
      About <span class="text-accent">Me</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <div class="border border-border p-6 hover:border-blue transition-colors">
        <div class="text-accent mb-2">// Education</div>
        <div class="text-sm">
          I hold a degree in Medical Education and am an alumnus of Purwadhika
          Digital Technology School's Web Development Bootcamp.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="border border-border p-6 hover:border-blue transition-colors">
        <div class="text-accent mb-2">// Problem-solving</div>
        <div class="text-sm">
          I approach challenges with a logical and systemic mindset.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="border border-border p-6 hover:border-blue transition-colors">
        <div class="text-accent mb-2">// Experience</div>
        <div class="text-sm">I have a diverse portfolio of projects.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="border border-border p-6 hover:border-blue transition-colors">
        <div class="text-accent mb-2">// Technical Skill</div>
        <div class="text-sm">
          As a Fullstack Web Developer, I specialize in React JS and Tailwind
          CSS. My expertise extends to backend technologies, including Express
          JS for server-side development, SQL databases for efficient data
          management, TypeScript for enhanced code quality, and Golang for
          high-performance applications.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <DownloadButton client:load />
  </div>
</section>
